    "<a id='p2'></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "## Problema 02\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Sea $\\sigma(n)$ definido como la suma de los divisores propios de $n$ (n√∫meros menores que n que se dividen en $n$).\n",
    "\n",
    "Los [n√∫meros amigos](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amicable_numbers) son  enteros positivos $n_1$ y $n_2$ tales que la suma de los divisores propios de uno es igual al otro n√∫mero y viceversa, es decir, $\\sigma(n_1)=\\sigma(n_2)$ y $\\sigma(n_2)=\\sigma(n_1)$.\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Por ejemplo, los n√∫meros 220 y 284 son n√∫meros amigos.\n",
    "* los divisores propios de 220 son 1, 2, 4, 5, 10, 11, 20, 22, 44, 55 y 110; por lo tanto $\\sigma(220) = 284$. \n",
    "* los divisores propios de 284 son 1, 2, 4, 71 y 142; entonces $\\sigma(284) = 220$.\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "Implemente una funci√≥n llamada `amigos` cuyo input sean dos n√∫meros naturales $n_1$ y $n_2$, cuyo output sea verifique si los n√∫meros son amigos o no.\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Ejemplo**: *amigos(220,284)* = True, *amigos(6,5)* = False\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Definir Funci√≥n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def amigos(n,m:int):\n",
    "    \n",
    "     \n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    calcular_amigos(n,m)\n",
    "\n",
    "    Implemente una funci√≥n llamada amigos cuyo input sean dos n√∫meros naturales  ùëõ1  y  ùëõ2 , cuyo output sea verifique \n",
    "    si los n√∫meros son amigos o no.\n",
    "\n",
    "    Parameters\n",
    "    ----------\n",
    "    n : int\n",
    "        Numero amigo 1.\n",
    "    m: int\n",
    "        Numero amigo 2.\n",
    "\n",
    "    Returns\n",
    "    -------\n",
    "    output : Valor l√≥gico\n",
    "        \n",
    "    Examples\n",
    "    --------\n",
    "    >>> amigos(220,284)\n",
    "    True\n",
    "    \n",
    "    >>> amigos(6,5) \n",
    "    False\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    \n",
    "    e = 1 # valor incial\n",
    "    suma_n_multiplos=0\n",
    "    suma_m_multiplos=0\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for k in range(1,n):\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if n%k==0:\n",
    "            suma_n_multiplos+=k\n",
    "        \n",
    "    for k in range(1,m):\n",
    "        \n",
    "        if m%k==0:\n",
    "            suma_m_multiplos+=k\n",
    "        \n",
    "    if suma_m_multiplos==n and suma_n_multiplos==m:\n",
    "        return True\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return False\n",
    "        \n",
    "        \n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Verificar ejemplos"
